items.name: whisper-pair-app
items.description: WhisperPair is a defensive security research tool that demonstrates the CVE-2025-36911 vulnerability in Google's Fast Pair protocol. This vulnerability affects millions of Bluetooth audio devices worldwide, allowing unauthorized pairing and potential microphone access without user consent.
